{"tid":1192508,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【患腦腫瘤】陳振華大仔無綫配音員陳廷軒 美國接受手術期間離世終年49歲","createTime":"2019-06-08T12:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T14:27:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2987a2e1e1b9ecc21df4a2acca5c5e4374331ca","tid":1192508,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190608/large/1559992891_eaa9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190608%2Flarge%2F1559992891_eaa9.jpg&h=43455170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n70年代無綫第一代小生陳振華，去年1月病逝，終年78歲。離逝後其家人據其遺願，將他遺體送往香港大學做大體老師，十分大愛（相關新聞︰ <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2EYxWsa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2EYxWsa&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSaxOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=6955a98d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2EYxWsa</a> ）。<br />\n<br />\n曾開班教配音的陳振華，他兩位兒子陳廷軒、陳樂文繼承其衣缽，在無綫任職配音員。日前《蘋果》收到消息指，陳振華的大兒子陳廷軒，因腦部有腫瘤到美國醫治，可惜上月在美國接受第二次手術後，不幸離世，終年49歲。<br />\n<br />\n據陳廷軒的同業表示，現職無綫配音員的陳廷軒，於2017年尾發現腦部有腫瘤，導致影響視力，當時他向公司辭配，一直由他配開的韓國綜藝節目《Running Man》中池石鎮一角。他於2018年1月向公司請長病假，遠赴美國就醫，經過第一次手術成功後，休養至年底才重返工作崗位。據其同業透露︰「佢上個月左右再去美國做第二次手術，好似話佢手術期間頂唔住走咗。」<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n而今日在網上都有網民談及陳廷軒離世的消息，《蘋果》致電丁羽叔了解，身在大陸的丁羽叔說︰「我知道佢有呢個病，要去美國做手術，但我未知道佢走咗，等我返香港了解。」"},{"pid":"72627e9d3b43cea12ea8468082d924cc79107a5e","tid":1192508,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:44:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190608/59692434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190608%2F59692434&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSaxOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=27064270\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190608%2F59692434&h=bc18379e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190608/59692434</a>"},{"pid":"da225b91abd26543683e11fe476ba90e117aebcf","tid":1192508,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:46:53.000Z","msg":"因為佢我先鐘意池石鎮<br />\n無左佢配已經完全唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d990d06963c6e866cd73da8eb58f8a37d88b0a","tid":1192508,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"鬼塚英吉佢配得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97585e6f5423c7762470b88615aec5495914230","tid":1192508,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c7dd80bb8f7d6e5e6f8c6ddb106c946dfe5399","tid":1192508,"uid":193693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:46:27.000Z","msg":"係唔係小丸子個旁白？"},{"pid":"92113092090d06ec4e1bf0fe7518f1e046fe68fa","tid":1192508,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5c7dd80bb8f7d6e5e6f8c6ddb106c946dfe5399","tid":1192508,"uid":193693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:46:27.000Z","msg":"係唔係小丸子個旁白？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:47:58.000Z","msg":"果個係戰鬥陳欣獸，仲後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8d9aa00da906787b9f17b8fc2ca90074c126f8","tid":1192508,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T14:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4x2CHv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4x2CHv.png&h=859dda5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BrDk8Pb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht